Load survey

Source: R/load_survey.R
load_survey.Rd

Load survey

Usage

load_survey(
  path = NULL,
  svy_type = NULL,
  svy_edition = NULL,
  svy_weight = NULL,
  svy_psu = NULL,
  ...
)

Arguments

path

Path to the survey file

svy_type

Type of survey

svy_edition

Edition of the survey

svy_weight

Weight of the survey

svy_psu

Primary sampling unit

...

Additional arguments

Value

Survey object

Examples

set_engine("data.table")
#> Engine: data.table
svy_example <- load_survey(
  "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/metasurveyr/metasurvey_data/main/eaii/2019-2021.csv",
  svy_type = "eaii",
  svy_edition = "2019-2021",
  svy_weight = add_weight(annual = "w_trans"),
  dec = ","
)
svy_example
#> Type: EAII
#> Edition: 2019_2021
#> Periodicity: Trianual
#> Engine: data.table
#> Design:    
#> * ANNUAL ESTIMATION
#>         
#> * Package: survey
#> * Variance estimation: Ultimate cluster
#>   * PSU: psu
#>   * Strata: NULL
#>   * Weight: w_trans
#>   * FPC: NULL
#>   * Calibrate formula: ~1
#> Steps: None
#> Recipes: None
